<h2 id="gp">Gaussian Process</h2>
<p>Consider a model defined in terms of a linear combination of $M$ fixed basis functions given by the elements of the vecotr $\phi(x)$ so that
\begin{equation}
y(x)=w^T\phi(x)
\end{equation}</p>

